.TITLE Code - Result

.cast.stream
.cast.block.show 8:10
.CAST
```
package main

import (
  "fmt"
  "time"
)

func main() {
  fmt.Println("hello")
  time.Sleep(3 * time.Second)
  fmt.Println("world")
}
```

.cut
- code is usually executed nad returned
- for streamed output add `.cast.stream` lin in front of code
